<title>ARE YOUR WINDOWS OPEN?</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hebrai mi sal khupdinpa kha na mu'm?
 Zing, sun leh zana paucham kha?
 A indan ah Zion a hezing a,
 Gamla saltang himahleh.

[V2]
 Jerusalem lam ngan tukvan na hawng em?
 Ziehin saltang bangin &quot;chawmkhat&quot; um mah leng;
 Lalpen lopi taka thuoma hung ding chuh,
 Nicheng in na ngakzing em?

[V3]
 2. Meipi-a paihlut ding chuh lau kiu in,
 Sakei-baknei kula khiek le;
 Daniel Pathien in hun hukdawk ina,
 Angelte hun sawl in tin.

[V4]
 3. Pathien hing chate haw hangsan unla,
 Na suohchak lau kipakin sau;
 Zion tangpi lam chuh nga chiet unla,
 Lalpen hung chuh tuok dingin.</lyrics>
</song>